 Fix got married to Orrock Robertsen on Friday on a farm in Barkly East, Eastern Cape.According to one of the guests Simone Bosman on Instagram, the theme of the wedding was farm style glam and the groom decorated the venue himself. The theme of the wedding was farm style glam...the venue was a perfect fit. The LOVE sign, under which the couple were married stood, was made by the groom, Bosman wrote on Instagram. Yesterday was all sorts of magical to witness Fix getting married. [The] Bride is beyond beautiful, the groom very dapper, the venue (which the groom decorated) was stunning. Fix stunned in a white sheath gown, with a cleavage-hugging keyhole and ethereal cape.Top Billing presenter Maps Maponyane was one of the guests.